      "content": "hey, my chest is feeling kinda tight and burning kinda bad right now. i had a huge pizza dinner earlier so i think it might just be bad indigestion or heartburn... the discomfort is even kind of going down my left arm a bit. should i just take some extra strength antacids and wait it out?",
